  "description": "Why Local Transcript Parsing Matters for Data Privacy: a straight comparison for tax professionals, with trade-offs, pitfalls, and a CTA to generate a transcript report.",
  "content": "<section>\n        <h2 id=\"what-youre-comparing\" class=\"section-heading\">What You’re Comparing</h2>\n        <p class=\"article-text\">This page compares two common approaches tax professionals use to interpret transcripts. The goal is clarity: trade-offs, not hype.</p>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"trade-offs\" class=\"section-heading\">Trade-Offs That Matter</h2>\n        <div class=\"card-glass card-hover p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Accuracy: can you consistently explain sequences and timing?</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Privacy: does the workflow require uploading taxpayer data?</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Repeatability: can staff follow the same steps and get the same output?</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Speed: can you deliver a clean summary without burning billable hours?</span></li>\n        </ul>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"common-pitfalls\" class=\"section-heading\">Common Pitfalls</h2>\n        <div class=\"card-glass p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n         <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Common pitfalls</h3>\n         <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Assuming “cloud” automatically means better (it often means risk).</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Comparing features instead of outcomes (speed, clarity, privacy).</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Skipping client deliverables and relying on verbal explanations.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Treating transcript review as a one-off instead of a productized workflow.</span></li>\n         </ul>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"cta-parser\" class=\"section-heading\">Use a Client-Ready Report</h2>\n        <p class=\"article-text\">When the goal is a clean deliverable, you want a workflow that produces consistent output. Generate a transcript report in minutes.</p>\n        <div class=\"mt-6\">\n         <a href=\"/#how-it-works\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center\">Parse Transcript Now</a>\n        </div>\n       </section>",
